                    <head><hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi></head>
                    <p>On July 15, President <persName corresp="#p_TRUMANHS1">Truman</persName>
                        signed H.R, 8370 (Public Law 82–547; 66 Stat. 637), the Supplemental
                        Appropriation Act of 1953, which included an appropriation of $2,986,894,000
                        for the United States Atomic Energy Commission.</p>
                </div>
